categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Ogan-Dei was a Weequay male Jedi Master during the Galactic War. He was one of the leader of the Strike Team Oricon, a unit composed of members of the Jedi Order and the Republic Military that were dispatched to the moon of Oricon to eliminate the Dread Masters.
Ogan-Dei was one of the Jedi leaders to survive the initial approach to Oricon.
Ogan-Dei is a non-player character from the massively multi-player online role playing game Star Wars: The Old Republic released by BioWare in 2011. He is voiced by Fred Tatasciore.
